name: Bright red bracelet 1
description:
This bracelet is made out of bright red/dark pink polyester/silk wires and is finished with silver colored iron ribbon details.
On the frond, in between the wires, is a red metallic polyester ornament, melted into the shape of the seeds of an alien looking water plant.
On the frond, lower and upper part, are 2 silver colored details of a watch (the round detail on the side of a watch where you change the time with)
The toggle is a silver colored elastic watch strap.
This piece is unique and handcrafted and is very much a statement piece.

The size/circumference of the bracelet is 16/17 cm (6.3/6.69 inch)
The height of the piece is 7 cm (2.8 inch)
